# Pipeline working directory (`<app>/.dagent/<slug>/`) — slug folders are
# tracked in Git so PR reviewers can audit pipeline state alongside the
# feature diff. Only transient junk that pollutes the working dir
# (stray scripts an agent might emit at the slug root) is ignored.
.dagent/*.mjs
.dagent/*.js
.dagent/*.ts
